Package: slowhttptest
Version: 1.9.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: git, openssl, build-essential, findutils
Section: net
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/shekyan/slowhttptest
Description: Application Layer Denial of Service attack simulator
 slowhttptest is a tool to test the vulnerability of web servers to
 slow HTTP attacks (Slowloris, Slow POST, Slow Read, etc.).
